{"word":"G2687 - καταστέλλω - katastéllō - kat-as-tel'-lo - Appease","slug":"G2687","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταστέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>katastéllō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-as-tel'-lo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Appease"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>καταστέλλω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Katastello</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>kat-as-tel'-lo</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to send or put down, to lower </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to put or keep down one who is roused or incensed, to repress, restrain, appease, quiet </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G4724\">G4724</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 16:55,1 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G4724\">G4724</a>; to <i>put down</i> that is <b><i>quell</i></b>: - appease quiet. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1291\">G1291</a>, <a href=\"#/G1293\">G1293</a>, <a href=\"#/G1989\">G1989</a>, <a href=\"#/G1992\">G1992</a>, <a href=\"#/G2689\">G2689</a>, <a href=\"#/G4724\">G4724</a>, <a href=\"#/G4958\">G4958</a>, <a href=\"#/G5288\">G5288</a>, <a href=\"#/G5289\">G5289</a>"}]}